desc:
Origami would be the artwork of creating things in the world from 2D to 3D with a single sheet of paper. Before a single sheet of paper takes on the shape of the world, it must go through the process of folding and unfolding at least dozens or hundreds of times. The moment when someone I loved folded the paper for me was like magic. The sound of paper folding and unfolding and the gently moving fingers were enough to catch my attention. A single piece of paper has become a bird's wing, a wolf's leg, or a wizard's hat. 
You can do it with a piece of paper and Paper Crafts 1101 Origami Tutorial YouTube channel. Paper Wizard!!! If you don't give up until the last step:)
